<p><b>Henri-Louis Bergson</b> (<small>IPA</small>:&#160;<span title="Pronunciation in IPA" class="IPA"><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:IPA" title="Wikipedia:IPA">[bɛʁkˈsɔn]</a></span>; 18 October 1859–4 January 1941) was a <a href="/wiki/French_philosophy" title="French philosophy">French philosopher</a>, influential in the first half of the 20th century.</p>
