<li><i><a href="/wiki/Matter_and_Memory" title="Matter and Memory">Matter and Memory</a></i> 1911. (Matière et mémoire 1896) Zone Books 1990: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0942299051" class="internal">ISBN 0-942299-05-1</a>, Dover Publications 2004: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/048643415X" class="internal">ISBN 0-486-43415-X</a></li>
<li><i>Laughter: An Essay on the Meaning of the Comic</i> 1901. (Le rire) Green Integer 1998: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1892295024" class="internal">ISBN 1-892295-02-4</a>, Dover Publications 2005: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0486443809" class="internal">ISBN 0-486-44380-9</a></li>
